{"tid":1575684,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［獅鳥］大家只係自衛   唔好主動出手","createTime":"2019-09-17T02:36:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-21T17:29:21.000Z","uid":54186,"like":68,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"ce059cd3a2bc5cd431e2f2e1808cc77ed75bc635","tid":1575684,"uid":54186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T02:36:23.000Z","msg":"係心默諗十次<br />\n<br />\n自衛反擊  合情合理合法<br />\n<br />\n但一主動出手  隨時步黃背心後塵<br />\n<br />\n請緊記<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef343bc1f29f37e272c3fae3dbff4d3e1bfcbbb9","tid":1575684,"uid":54186,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T02:39:57.000Z","msg":"藍絲eq咁低實會主動出手"},{"pid":"5af9d45d5852ac93ef1af91ce5ee1fcedced1b65","tid":1575684,"uid":54186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T02:40:10.000Z","msg":"推推推"},{"pid":"4957b5d00dda29dd062e6b066c3969557d3ca059","tid":1575684,"uid":52621,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T02:40:51.000Z","msg":"唔好佢推你打你一下就即刻還手<br />\n佢推你第一下 開始多CAM影埋黎<br />\n你即還擊 好多CAM就得你打佢<br />\n另外我相信有人係會收錢搏打<br />\n外媒無可能完全知道來龍去脈，即使本地媒體都係一樣<br />\n香港唔同其他地方<br />\n要食糊要拉埋外國先食到<br />\n所以還擊幾下就夠 出黎片段好睇D<br />\n打到重傷只有自己爽 嚇唔到藍屍的 佢地只覺得英勇受傷"},{"pid":"16a2d7cb6728d0200fead2fc65dbf3558eeb3570","tid":1575684,"uid":198684,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T02:41:31.000Z","msg":"tui，先撩者賤，所以我地唔好做先撩人果個，但俾人撩就一定要出手自保！<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56bef05d850ece012c970338e18086473fff80dd","tid":1575684,"uid":140326,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T02:43:21.000Z","msg":"有組織 收何君堯錢 破壞連儂牆 果D黑社會點計？"},{"pid":"2c6eff39dd2b774ae50df6ea55cc98347723c42c","tid":1575684,"uid":140326,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{